%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20OpenAI%20job%20listing%20described%20ambitions%20to%20build%20an%20ad%20network.%20Then%20the%20company%20deleted%20the%20references.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224097%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CEO%20of%20OpenAI%20Sam%20Altman%20speaks%20to%20members%20of%20the%20media%20as%20he%20arrives%20at%20the%20Sun%20Valley%20l%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a4d949994175b768171fefc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222765%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESam%20Altman's%20OpenAI%20has%20been%20building%20up%20its%20ad%20business.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20version%20of%20this%20post%20appears%20in%20the%20CMO%20Insider%20newsletter.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESign%20up%20for%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Fcmo-insider%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20weekly%20marketing%20newsletter%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20OpenAI%20job%20listing%20hints%20that%20the%20AI%20giant%20is%20laying%20the%20groundwork%20for%20an%20ad%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-slow-motion-advertising-rollout-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenAI's%20nascent%20ad%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20a%20platform%20for%20advertisers%20looking%20to%20reach%20ChatGPT%20users.%20Now%2C%20there's%20evidence%20that%20the%20AI%20giant%20might%20want%20to%20jump%20into%20a%20new%20side%20of%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20helping%20publishers%20and%20other%20companies%20sell%20their%20own%20ad%20space%20to%20marketers%2C%20CMO%20Insider%20can%20exclusively%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjobs.ashbyhq.com%2Fopenai%2F0875c19f-3f37-403e-81e9-7bf2429f1e4e%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20job%20ad%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20last%20week%2C%20called%20for%20a%20%26quot%3Bsupport%20delivery%20lead%26quot%3B%20in%20its%20ads%20division.%20The%20job%20posting%2C%20which%20OpenAI%20modified%20after%20CMO%20Insider%20asked%20about%20it%2C%20referenced%20building%20a%20publisher-facing%20ad%20business%2C%20the%20first%20time%20the%20company%20has%20publicly%20mentioned%20ambitions%20in%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20move%20could%20boost%20ad%20revenue%2C%20offer%20marketers%20placements%20beyond%20the%20ChatGPT%20app%2C%20and%20potentially%20soothe%20tensions%20with%20some%20publishers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20huge%20sign%20that%20OpenAI%20is%20building%20toward%20an%20advertising%20business%20far%20beyond%20just%20ChatGPT%2C%26quot%3B%20Debra%20Aho%20Williamson%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20AI-focused%20research%20and%20advisory%20firm%20Sonata%20Insights%2C%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20posting%20originally%20said%20that%20the%20role's%20publisher-side%20responsibilities%20would%20include%20%26quot%3Binventory%20setup%2C%20ad%20serving%20integrations%2C%20reporting%2C%20and%20yield-impacting%20issues.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20person%20would%20%26quot%3Bdesign%20and%20continuously%20improve%20support%20coverage%20for%20both%20ad%20buyers%20and%20publishers%2C%20ensuring%20the%20team%20can%20diagnose%20buyer-side%20delivery%20issues%20and%20publisher-side%20monetization%20and%20integration%20issues%20with%20equal%20rigor%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20job%20posting%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20updated%20the%20job%20ad%20after%20CMO%20Insider%20contacted%20the%20company%20about%20it%2C%20removing%20references%20to%20publishers.%20The%20company%20deleted%20or%20edited%20five%20sentences%20in%20the%20posting.%20OpenAI%20later%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Esaid%20the%20role's%20responsibilities%20cover%20agencies%20and%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIntriguing!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20could%20an%20OpenAI%20ad%20network%20look%20like%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20job%20ad%20didn't%20fully%20sketch%20out%20what%20OpenAI%20is%20interested%20in%20building.%20The%20most%20obvious%20move%20for%20OpenAI%20would%20be%20to%20enter%20the%20world%20of%20%26quot%3Bdemand%20extension%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Baudience%20extension.%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20could%20take%20growing%20advertiser%20demand%20and%20extend%20those%20campaigns%20to%20placements%20on%20a%20network%20of%20external%20websites%20or%20apps.%20Publishers%20would%20be%20able%20to%20monetize%20their%20own%20traffic%20using%20the%20commercial%20signals%20gathered%20by%20ChatGPT.%20Think%20of%20it%20as%20an%20AI-native%20equivalent%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffacebook-just-had-some-layoffs-heres-why-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFacebook%20Audience%20Network%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20Google%20Display%20Network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20told%20CMO%20Insider%20it%20isn't%20entering%20demand%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStrategically%2C%20creating%20an%20ad%20network%20would%20make%20sense%20for%20OpenAI%2C%20though%20it%20would%20represent%20an%20unusually%20fast%20jump%20into%20supply-side%20adtech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20biggest%20advertiser%20gripes%20with%20OpenAI's%20ad%20product%20so%20far%20is%20that%20advertiser%20demand%20has%20outpaced%20available%20supply.%20Advertisers%20previously%20complained%20that%20OpenAI%20had%20been%20slow%20to%20actually%20spend%20their%20budgets%2C%20despite%20asking%20for%20hefty%20upfront%20commitments%20to%20participate%20in%20early%20ad%20trials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI's%20head%20of%20global%20ad%20solutions%2C%20Dave%20Dugan%2C%20told%20me%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenais-dave-dugan-explains-the-strategy-behind-chatgpt-ads-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20June%20interview%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20ad%20delivery%20and%20volume%20had%20improved%20as%20its%20confidence%20in%20the%20ChatGPT%20Ads%20user%20experience%20had%20grown.%20Still%2C%20OpenAI%20only%20serves%20ads%20to%20users%20on%20ChatGPT's%20free%20or%20lower-priced%20tiers%20in%20select%20regions%2C%20meaning%20its%20native%20ad%20real%20estate%20remains%20fundamentally%20constrained%20by%20the%20chat%20interface.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20publisher%20ad%20network%20could%20help%20with%20the%20inventory%20bottleneck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2286ae709d-b077-447c-8df5-86ef21fdb02f%5C%22%3EBuilding%20bridges%20with%20publishers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELaunching%20a%20sell-side%20product%20would%20also%20mark%20a%20dramatic%20shift%20in%20OpenAI's%20relationship%20with%20media%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20date%2C%20publishers%20do%20not%20receive%20a%20cut%20of%20ChatGPT's%20ad%20revenue.%20Instead%2C%20some%20publishers%20make%20money%20from%20OpenAI%20through%20direct%20licensing%20deals%20for%20training%20data%20and%20content%20retrieval.%20(Business%20Insider%20parent%20company%2C%20Axel%20Springer%2C%20has%20one%20of%20these%20deals.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20broader%20relationship%20remains%20tense%3A%20publishers%20including%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-new-york-times-copyright-infringement-lawsuit-chatgpt-logs-private-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Ziff%20Davis%2C%20and%20a%20coalition%20of%20local%20news%20outlets%20are%20actively%20suing%20OpenAI%2C%20alleging%20copyright%20infringement.%20OpenAI%20has%20argued%20that%20its%20training%20of%20AI%20models%20is%20protected%20by%20the%20fair%20use%20doctrine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20ad%20network%20would%20introduce%20a%20new%20way%20for%20OpenAI%20to%20compensate%20publishers%2C%20giving%20them%20a%20cut%20of%20ad%20revenue%20if%20a%20user%20views%20or%20clicks%20an%20ad%20served%20on%20their%20site%20or%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20OpenAI%20prepares%20for%20an%20eventual%20public%20offering%2C%20it%20faces%20pressure%20to%20scale%20high-margin%20revenue%20streams%2C%20such%20as%20ads.%20The%20company%20must%20justify%20its%20eye-popping%20private%20valuation%20and%20offset%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20in%20long-term%20compute%20and%20infrastructure%20commitments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20Axios%20reported%20that%20OpenAI%20was%20forecasting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.axios.com%2F2026%2F04%2F09%2Fopenai-100-billion-in-ad-revenue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabout%20%242.5%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20ad%20revenue%20in%202026%20and%20around%20%24100%20billion%20in%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENate%20Elliott%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20BI's%20sister%20company%20EMARKETER%2C%20said%20that%20for%20OpenAI%20to%20hit%20those%20numbers%2C%20it%20would%20need%20to%20dramatically%20expand%20its%20user%20base%2C%20charge%20top-tier%20ad%20rates%2C%20and%20potentially%20risk%20ruining%20the%20user%20experience%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-projects-chatgpt-ad-growth-market-doubts-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eheavy%20ad%20load%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOr%2C%20it%20could%20build%20an%20ad%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-job-listing-publisher-ad-network-monetization-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784689201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5f9f6fce52cb26b8391e48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-job-listing-publisher-ad-network-monetization-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20OpenAI%20job%20listing%20hinted%20at%20ambitions%20to%20build%20%26quot%3Bpublisher-side%20monetization%26quot%3B%20tools.%20OpenAI%20edited%20the%20ad%20after%20we%20asked%20about%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22loreilly%40insider.com%20(Lara%20O'Reilly)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indian%20diplomats%20at%20UN%20mission%20still%20displaced%20three%20weeks%20after%20building%20evacuation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784687820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132549961%2Cimgsize-922078.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-diplomats-at-un-mission-still-displaced-three-weeks-after-building-evacuation%2Farticleshow%2F132549942.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132549942.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-diplomats-at-un-mission-still-displaced-three-weeks-after-building-evacuation%2Farticleshow%2F132549942.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-diplomats-at-un-mission-still-displaced-three-weeks-after-building-evacuation%2Famp_articleshow%2F132549942.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-diplomats-at-un-mission-still-displaced-three-weeks-after-building-evacuation%2Famp_articleshow%2F132549942.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20probing%20Harvard%20over%20financial%20aid%20programmes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784687784000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-132549935%2Cimgsize-1434453.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fus-probing-harvard-over-financial-aid-programmes%2Farticleshow%2F132549885.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132549885.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engage