0Park%2C%20New%20York.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784679123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-07%2F159dcvvs_iran-attack-on-jordan_625x300_18_July_26.jpeg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1280%2Cheight%3D720%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-identifies-3rd-american-soldier-believed-to-be-killed-in-iran-attack-11803656%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20military%20has%20confirmed%20that%20a%20third%20service%20member%20is%20believed%20to%20be%20dead%20in%20Friday's%20attack%20on%20a%20base%20in%20Jordan%20and%20identified%20them%20as%20Sgt.%20Angel%20S.%20Rampersad%2C%2028%2C%20of%20Ozone%20Park%2C%20New%20York.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-identifies-3rd-american-soldier-believed-to-be-killed-in-iran-attack-11803656%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-identifies-3rd-american-soldier-believed-to-be-killed-in-iran-attack-11803656%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-identifies-3rd-american-soldier-believed-to-be-killed-in-iran-attack-11803656%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Phone%20calls%20on%20flights%20could%20soon%20be%20banned.%20Former%20flight%20attendants%20say%20it's%20about%20more%20than%20manners.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225184%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Passengers%20sit%20in%20an%20airplane%20cabin%20with%20rows%20of%20seatback%20screens%20and%20overhead%20monitors%20visible.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5ff346ce52cb26b83921f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223456%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20flight%20attendants%20say%20in-flight%20phone%20calls%20can%20be%20distracting%20to%20other%20passengers%20and%20crew.%3Cp%3ECrist%C3%B3bal%20Alvarado%20Minic%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELawmakers%20introduced%20a%20bill%20to%20ban%20phone%20calls%20on%20flights.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFormer%20flight%20attendants%20say%20the%20rule%20would%20benefit%20crew%20and%20passengers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPhone%20calls%20on%20flights%20have%20been%20allowed%20by%20some%20airlines%20as%20in-flight%20WiFi%20becomes%20more%20common.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETalking%20on%20the%20phone%20and%20smoking%20cigarettes%20could%20soon%20share%20something%20in%20common%3A%20being%20legally%20banned%20on%20airplanes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20bill%20introduced%20by%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20House%20of%20Representatives%20last%20month%20would%20make%20taking%20phone%20or%20video%20calls%20from%20the%20air%20illegal%2C%20an%20issue%20that's%20becoming%20increasingly%20relevant%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-airline-wifi-is-no-longer-special-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWiFi%20access%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20skies%20expands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20flight%20attendants%20say%20talking%20on%20the%20phone%20inside%20a%20plane%20is%20already%20against%20the%20policies%20of%20some%20airlines%2C%20but%20making%20it%20the%20law%20would%20protect%20passengers%20as%20well%20as%20the%20flight%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20shoved%20into%20a%20tin%20can%2C%20and%20we're%20hurdling%20through%20the%20sky%20at%2038%2C000%20feet.%20It's%20not%20a%20normal%20situation%20to%20be%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Ally%20Murphy%2C%20a%20former%20flight%20attendant%20and%20cabin%20service%20supervisor%20at%20Virgin%20Atlantic%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20with%20somebody%20and%20having%20to%20speak%20loudly%2C%20you're%20really%20disrupting%20the%20other%20passengers%20around%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECongress%20voted%20in%202018%20to%20require%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffaa-video-warns-passengers-leave-bags-behind-airline-emergency-evacuations-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFederal%20Aviation%20Administration%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20ban%20phone%20calls%20on%20flights%2C%C2%A0but%20did%20not%20set%20a%20deadline%2C%20and%20a%20ban%20has%20never%20been%20implemented.%20The%20Quiet%20Skies%20Act%2C%20introduced%20by%20Democratic%20Reps.%20Greg%20Stanton%20and%20Hillary%20Scholten%2C%20and%20Republican%20Reps.%20Rick%20Crawford%20and%20Rob%20Bresnahan%20would%20force%20the%20FAA%20to%20finalize%20the%20ban%20within%20180%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Congress%20rarely%20legislates%20airplane%20etiquette%20%E2%80%94%20airlines%20are%20generally%20able%20to%20set%20their%20own%20policies%20%E2%80%94%20the%20government%20has%20stepped%20in%20on%20matters%20related%20to%20health%20and%20safety%2C%20or%20security%20concerns%2C%20such%20as%20banning%20smoking%20and%20vaping%20or%20requiring%20masks%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20that%20happens%20in%20the%20aviation%20industry%2C%20the%20underlying%20first%20thought%20will%20always%20be%20about%20how%20does%20this%20affect%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20aircraft%20and%20the%20passengers%20who%20are%20on%20board%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPassengers%20talking%20loudly%20on%20the%20phone%20or%20FaceTiming%20a%20friend%20could%20be%20a%20distraction%2C%20especially%20if%20other%20passengers%20lodge%20complaints%20with%20the%20crew%2C%20and%20could%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20passengers%20to%20hear%20crew%20announcements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22591a6937-69e8-46fb-8312-6efc35d30d08%5C%22%3EA%20universal%20ban%20could%20help%20flight%20attendants%20avoid%20conflict%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20major%20American%20airlines%2C%20including%20United%2C%20American%2C%20and%20Southwest%2C%20prohibit%20in-flight%20phone%20calls%2C%20British%20Airways%20earlier%20this%20year%20said%20it%20would%20allow%20phone%20and%20video%20calls%20on%20aircraft%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairlines-starlink-wifi-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarlink%20WiFi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Virgin%20Atlantic%20also%20allows%20phone%20calls%20on%20its%20Starlink-equipped%20flights%2C%20though%20it%20asks%20that%20they%20be%20kept%20short%2C%20and%20it%20does%20not%20allow%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBobby%20Laurie%2C%20a%20former%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-you-should-avoid-buying-planes-airports-flight-attendant-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eflight%20attendant%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20travel%20industry%20expert%2C%20said%20inconsistent%20or%20ambiguous%20rules%20can%20be%20confusing%20for%20passengers%20and%20difficult%20for%20flight%20attendants%20to%20enforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20put%20crew%20in%20a%20tricky%20position%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20make%20subjective%20calls%20about%20what%20constitutes%20disruptive%20behavior%2C%20in%20turn%20increasing%20the%20potential%20for%20conflict%20between%20flight%20attendants%20and%20passengers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20ask%20people%20to%20be%20considerate%2C%20consideration%20means%20something%20different%20for%20everybody%2C%26quot%3B%20Laurie%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20a%20blanket%20ban%20could%20help%20flight%20attendants%20avoid%20the%20kinds%20of%20passenger%20confrontations%20that%20became%20more%20common%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Hudson%2C%20the%20president%20of%20FlyerRights%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20advocates%20for%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpassengers-lost-out-repayments-up-to-775-for-flight-delays-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eairline%20passengers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20he%20supports%20a%20ban%20on%20phone%20calls%20but%20that%20there%20could%20be%20some%20accommodations%2C%20such%20as%20a%20phone%20booth%20or%20a%20designated%20section%20where%20calls%20are%20allowed.%20Airlines%2C%20which%20have%20increasingly%20embraced%20a%20pay-for-every-amenity%20model%2C%20could%20charge%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20satisfy%20the%20need%20for%20people%20who%20want%20to%20do%20business%20or%20have%20family%20issues%2C%20especially%20on%20long%20flights%2C%20and%20also%20protect%20the%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20noting%20Amtrak%20trains%20have%20designated%20%26quot%3Bquiet%26quot%3B%20cars%20as%20well%20as%20cars%20where%20calls%20are%20allowed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20safety%20would%20generally%20be%20the%20primary%20consideration%20for%20a%20government-mandated%20ban%2C%20Jacqueline%20Whitmore%2C%20a%20former%20flight%20attendant%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-not-to-do-at-work-event-mistakes-etiquette-experts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eetiquette%20expert%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20talking%20on%20the%20phone%20while%20flying%20is%20often%20a%20matter%20of%20manners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20a%20finger's%20length%20from%20your%20seatmate%2C%20so%20they%20can%20hear%20every%20word%20you%20say%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20wants%20to%20hear%20your%20conversation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20occasional%20quiet%20phone%20call%20could%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20be%20made%20on%20a%20flight%20without%20causing%20issues%2C%20the%20former%20flight%20attendants%20said%20laws%20and%20policies%20often%20have%20to%20anticipate%20and%20prepare%20for%20the%20worst-case%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20always%20have%20to%20cater%20the%20rules%20and%20regulations%20towards%20the%20most%20troublesome%20person%20on%20the%20plane%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphone-call-ban-airplanes-flight-attendants-passengers-safety-etiquette-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784678189000%2C%22v