indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fishowspeeds-instagram-reel-featuring-bts-becomes-most-viewed-in-first-24-hours-with-300-million-views%2Farticleshow%2F132546605.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F132546605.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIShowSpeed's%20Instagram%20Reel%20of%20meeting%20BTS%20at%20the%20FIFA%20World%20Cup%202026%20final%20achieved%20a%20record.%20The%20viral%20video%20garnered%20an%20impressive%20300%20million%20views%20within%20its%20initial%20twenty-four%20hours.%20This%20encounter%20brought%20together%20a%20major%20streamer%20and%20a%20popular%20K-pop%20group%2C%20creating%20significant%20buzz.%20Fans%20worldwide%20rapidly%20shared%20the%20clip%2C%20contributing%20to%20its%20immense%20popularity%20and%20viral%20spread.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sumit%20Roy%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fishowspeeds-instagram-reel-featuring-bts-becomes-most-viewed-in-first-24-hours-with-300-million-views%2Farticleshow%2F132546605.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fishowspeeds-instagram-reel-featuring-bts-becomes-most-viewed-in-first-24-hours-with-300-million-views%2Famp_articleshow%2F132546605.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fishowspeeds-instagram-reel-featuring-bts-becomes-most-viewed-in-first-24-hours-with-300-million-views%2Famp_articleshow%2F132546605.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20gastroenterologist.%20Here's%20how%20my%20family%20is%20eating%20during%20the%20cyclospora%20outbreak.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Headshot%20of%20gastroenterologist%20Stephen%20Chang%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5fa13754f9875261777bee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDr.%20Stephen%20Chang%2C%20a%20gastroenterologist%20at%20Northwestern%20Memorial%20Hospital%2C%20shares%20how%20his%20insights%20on%20how%20to%20stay%20safe%20amid%20the%20cyclospora%20outbreak.%3Cp%3ENorthwestern%20Medicine%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDr.%20Stephen%20Chang%20is%20a%20gastroenterologist%20at%20Northwestern%20Memorial%20Hospital%20in%20Illinois.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmid%20the%20cyclospora%20outbreak%2C%20he%20and%20his%20family%20haven't%20changed%20their%20eating%20habits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20advises%20practicing%20good%20food%20hygiene%20and%20being%20vigilant%20rather%20than%20forgoing%20all%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Dr.%20Stephen%20Chang%2C%20a%20gastroenterologist%20and%20the%20interim%20endoscopy%20director%20at%20Northwestern%20Memorial%20Hospital%20and%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20medicine%20at%20Northwestern%20University's%20Feinberg%20School%20of%20Medicine.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20cyclospora%20outbreak%2C%20my%20family%20hasn't%20changed%20what%20we're%20consuming%20or%20our%20eating%20practices.%20I%20have%20older%20children%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20want%20them%20to%20use%20this%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20stop%20eating%20fruits%20and%20vegetables.%20The%20teaching%20point%20in%20our%20house%20right%20now%20is%20reminding%20them%20about%20how%20to%20prepare%20them%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20for%20everybody%20to%20remember%20that%20we%20actually%20have%20had%20outbreaks%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faldi-hy-vee-bagged-salads-linked-illness-cdc-fda-say-2020-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecyclospora%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20bigger%20than%20what%20we've%20seen%20before%2C%20but%20the%20numbers%20are%20still%20relatively%20low%20overall.%20(As%20of%20late%20last%20week%2C%20just%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fchicago.suntimes.com%2Fnews%2F2026%2F07%2F14%2Fillinois-reports-216-cases-of-diarrhea-inducing-cyclosporiasis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E300%20confirmed%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20reported%20here%20in%20Illinois%2C%20and%20the%20state's%20population%20is%20over%2012%20million%20people.)%20It's%20much%20more%20likely%20for%20us%20to%20come%20across%20other%20causes%20of%20acute%20diarrhea%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-norovirus-spreads-cdc-symptoms-lysol-hand-sanitizer-stomach-bug-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elike%20norovirus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20E.%20Coli%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalmonella-outbreak-linked-to-raw-dough-3-people-in-hospital-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20Salmonella%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20than%20cyclospora.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20start%20having%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fman-got-diarrhea-parasite-cyclospora-symptoms-advice-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersistent%20symptoms%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20diarrhea%20lasting%20longer%20than%20a%20few%20days%20to%20up%20to%20a%20week%20%E2%80%94%20seek%20medical%20care%20and%20see%20if%20testing%20is%20appropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20advice%20I'm%20giving%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20about%20being%20vigilant%20about%20avoiding%20suspected%20sources%20of%20this%20outbreak%2C%20without%20completely%20changing%20our%20eating%20habits%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229fe3a748-d108-4c99-a2aa-822e5fd6865b%5C%22%3E1.%20Wash%20your%20veggies%20thoroughly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-salad-greens-safe-to-eat-cyclospora-experts-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esalad%20person%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Even%20before%20this%20cyclospora%20outbreak%2C%20I%20would%20usually%20still%20thoroughly%20wash%20my%20bagged%20salad%2C%20even%20if%20the%20packaging%20said%20it%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbagged-salad-food-poisoning-parasite-florida-cyclosporiasis-cdc-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epre-washed%20or%20triple-washed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20tried%20to%20be%20pretty%20good%20about%20food%20handling%2C%20and%20this%20situation%20has%20reminded%20me%20to%20wash%20my%20food%20a%20bit%20longer%20than%20I%20usually%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20good%20reminder%20of%20things%20we%20should%20always%20be%20doing%20for%20food%20safety%3A%20washing%20our%20hands%20both%20before%20and%20after%20working%20with%20food%2C%20very%20thoroughly%20washing%20our%20produce%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20splashing%20them%20in%20the%20water%20for%20a%20cursory%20couple%20of%20seconds%20%E2%80%94%20and%20discarding%20the%20outer%20leaves%20of%20a%20head%20of%20lettuce%20after%20you've%20washed%20it%20and%20making%20sure%20you're%20washing%20the%20inside%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBe%20sure%20to%20wash%20your%20vegetables%20%3Cem%3Ebefore%3C%2Fem%3E%20you%20cut%20them%2C%20to%20prevent%20the%20knife%20from%20spreading%20contamination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20consider%20leaning%20more%20toward%20well-cooked%20vegetables%20during%20the%20outbreak%20if%20you%20can%2C%20for%20a%20better%20chance%20of%20not%20getting%20sick.%20We%20know%20that%20cyclospora%20is%20killed%20when%20heated%20to%20at%20least%20158%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ad7bdd91-b57c-4ac6-b6db-071ea3c365db%5C%22%3E2.%20Be%20careful%20with%20lettuce%20for%20now%20%E2%80%94%20including%20when%20dining%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20we%20have%20narrower%20guidance%20in%20terms%20of%20one%20potential%20source%20%E2%80%94%20iceberg%20lettuce%2C%20specifically%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-taylor-farms-taco-bell-lettuce-supplier-cyclosporiasis-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaylor%20Farms%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20it%20might%20be%20worth%20giving%20some%20pause%20about%20purchasing%20iceberg%20lettuce%2C%20or%20at%20least%20knowing%20where%20it's%20sourced%20from.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E(Editor's%20note%3A%20The%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20has%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Ffood%2Foutbreaks-foodborne-illness%2Finvestigation-5-state-outbreak-cyclospora-illnesses-iceberg-lettuce-july-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eadvised%20consumers%20not%20to%20eat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20recalled%20Taylor%20Farms'%20lettuce%20products.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20a%20regular%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flettuce-lovers-are-confused-and-afraid-as-cyclospora-spreads-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eiceberg%20lettuce%20consumer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I'm%20watching%20the%20news%20closely%20to%20make%20sure%20I'm%20not%20purchasing%20from%20somewhere%20that%20might%20be%20a%20suspected%20source.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20careful%20when%20eating%20out%20may%20be%20the%20bigger%20issue%2C%20because%20when%20you're%20preparing%20food%20at%20home%2C%20you're%20the%20one%20who%20cleans%20the%20products%20to%20eat%20yourself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20really%20set%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsalad-chains-amid-cyclospora-outbreak-we-dont-serve-iceberg-lettuce-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsuming%20lettuce%20at%20a%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20you%20don't%20know%20where%20it's%20from%2C%20maybe%20ask%20the%20restaurant%20if%20they%20know%20where%20they%20get%20it%20from.%20Or%2C%20take%20a%20pass%20on%20that%20for%20now%2C%20and%20lean%20more%20toward%20the%20well-cooked%20vegetable%20options%20until%20we%20know%20this%20is%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a9ed8873-1d05-4622-8e8f-2061127dbe69%5C%22%3E3.%20Clean%20your%20fruit%20carefully%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBerries%20are%20tricky.%20Some%20past%20outbreaks%20have%20been%20tied%20to%20them%2C%20but%20we%20don't%20know%20that%20about%20the%20current%20outbreak%20yet.%20They're%20smaller%2C%20not%20easy%20to%20clean%20with%20a%20brush%2C%20and%20many%20contain%20fine%20hairs%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC11510488%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexperts%20think%3C%2Fa%3E%20cyclospora%20has%20an%20easier%20time%20sticking%20to.%20Be%20more%20vigilant%20about%20how%20you%20wash%20them%2C%20or%20maybe%20avoid%20them%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerally%2C%20even%20for%20fruits%20with%20a%20rind%2C%20you%20should%20still%20have%20to%20wash%20the%20exterior%20part%20very%20thoroughly%20%E2%80%94%20like%20with%20a%20clean%20produce%20brush%20%E2%80%94%20before%20you%20cut%20it.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20knife%20could%20theoretically%20carry%20the%20organisms%20into%20the%20interior%20part%20that%20you're%20planning%20on%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aed28e13-e3ee-4bb8-9e30-1386aa3078a4%5C%22%3E4.%20Higher-risk%20individuals%20should%20be%20more%20careful%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20higher-risk%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20those%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20hospitalized%20if%20they%20get%20sick%20%E2%80%94%20that%20need%20to%20be%20much%20more%20vigilant%20include%20people%20who%20are%20immunocompromised%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20and%20young%20children%20or%20infants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20one%20of%20those%20higher-risk%20groups%2C%20reduce%20your%20raw%20vegetable%20and%20fruit%20intake%20and%20consume%20vegetables%20that%20are%20cooked%20at%20safe%20temperatures%20until%20the%20outbreak%20appears%20to%20be%20over%2C%20to%20give%20you%20the%20best%20chance%20of%20not%20getting%20sick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b9d66c56-a544-4895-827a-68763a54b2be%5C%22%3E5.%20Stay%20on%20top%20of%20the%20news%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20sort%20of%20up%20in%20the%20air%20as%20far%20as%20how%20long%20this%20may%20continue%20to%20go%20on%20for.%20Outbreaks%20tend%20to%20be%20seasonal%20%E2%80%94%20with%20case%20counts%20going%20down%20after%20late%20August%20and%20into%20September%20%E2%80%94%20because%20of%20the%20temperature%20required%20to%20allow%20the%20infectious%20particles%20to%20become%20infectious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20can%20still%20be%20unpredictable.%20Everybody%20should%20be%20vigilant%2C%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20live%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcyclosporiasis-outbreak-map-diarrhea-parasite-what-states-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estates%20where%20the%20hot%20spots%3C%2Fa%3E%20seem%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20situation%20is%20moving%20so%20fast%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20follow%20the%20news%20on%20this.%20Follow%20public%20health%20investigators'%20findings%20and%20guidance%20through%20sources%20like%20your%20local%20public%20health%20department's%20website%2C%20the%20CDC%20website%2C%20and%20the%20Department%20of%20Public%20Health%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20still%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20this%2C%20and%20although%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20specific%20guidance%20about%20the%20source%20of%20the%20outbreak%2C%20we%20can%20still%20safely%20consume%20a%20lot%20of%20fruits%20and%20vegetables%20if%20we%20practice%20good%20food-handling%20habits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajanezhang%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ejanezhang%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgastroenterologist-dad-advice-cyclospora-outbreak-eati