quot%3BI%20see%20Paramount%20in%20the%20same%20light%20as%20Spirit%20Airlines%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20streaming%20staffer%20said.%20%26quot%3BRegulators%20didn't%20let%20JetBlue%20and%20Spirit%20Airlines%20merge.%20Now%20Spirit%20is%20bankrupt%2C%20and%20JetBlue%20is%20struggling.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20WBD%20employees%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20they're%20uneasy%20about%20what%20the%20deal%20may%20mean%20for%20the%20media%20industry%2C%20but%20that%20the%20acquisition%20would%20benefit%20them%20financially.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20both%20said%20they%20stood%20to%20considerably%20benefit%20from%20stock%20grants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBest%20case%20for%20me%20personally%20is%20the%20deal%20goes%20through%2C%20I%20get%20laid%20off%2C%20and%20get%20my%2015%20months%20of%20severance%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20veteran%20WBD%20staffer%20added.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20I%20just%20need%20to%20find%20something%20for%20a%20couple%20years%20before%20I%20retire.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpokespeople%20for%20Paramount%20and%20WBD%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223fdb0335-1273-4112-9941-3d618637a17b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Tired%20of%20mergers%20and%20chaos'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20has%20said%20it%20needs%20to%20join%20forces%20with%20WBD%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frob-bonta-interview-paramount-wbd-lawsuit-movie-theaters-cable-tv-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eform%20%26quot%3Ba%20stronger%20competitor%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20dominant%20streaming%20and%20technology%20platforms%2C%26quot%3B%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-great-netflix-youtube-convergence-is-here-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20and%20YouTube%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Ellison's%20company%20insists%20its%20mega-merger%20will%20allow%20it%20to%20produce%20more%20films%20and%20TV%20shows%20than%20it%20can%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20in%20Hollywood%20are%20skeptical%2C%20however.%20Top%20actors%20and%20directors%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-stars-oppose-paramount-warner-bros-discovery-deal-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoken%20out%20against%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Paramount-WBD%20deal%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20result%20in%20%26quot%3Bfewer%20opportunities%20for%20creators%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bfewer%20jobs%20across%20the%20production%20ecosystem.%26quot%3B%20The%20Writers%20Guild%20of%20America%20has%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Paramount%2C%20arguing%20that%20it%20violates%20antitrust%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Paramount%20employees%20who%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20deal%20primarily%20expressed%20concerns%20about%20the%20potential%20impact%20a%20merger%20of%20rivals%20would%20have%20on%20the%20media%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20indifferent%20to%20sticking%20around%20because%20I'm%20so%20burned%20out%2C%20but%20I%20would%20hate%20it%20if%20others%20lost%20a%20career%20they%20were%20passionate%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Paramount%20streaming%20staffer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20streaming%20manager%20who%20opposes%20the%20deal%20said%20they're%20%26quot%3Btired%20of%20mergers%20and%20chaos.%26quot%3B%20Paramount%20merged%20with%20Skydance%20last%20August%2C%20six%20years%20after%20Viacom%20and%20CBS%20merged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20future%20in%20this%20deal%20is%20uncertain%2C%20I%20feel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20third%20streaming%20staffer%20who's%20against%20the%20merger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e15b720-db92-4e99-9818-eb029bbd0825%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'The%20best%20shot%20at%20keeping%20my%20job%20long%20term'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Paramount%20staffers%20who%20support%20the%20deal%20had%20a%20simple%20rationale%3A%20they%20believe%20the%20merger%20would%20be%20best%20for%20the%20company%20and%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20I%20may%