0with%20the%20AI%20hardware%20trade%20despite%20major%20volatility%20in%20chips%20stocks%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225573%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22AI%20server%20racks%20are%20displayed%20during%20the%20Nvidia%20Product%20Showcase%20at%20Computex%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5fbbcf548c9c486b30ea60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223715%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EI-Hwa%20Cheng%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChip%20stocks%20have%20seen%20major%20volatility%2C%20briefly%20tumbling%20into%20a%20bear%20market%20this%20month%20before%20rebounding.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20blurry%20rate%20outlook%2C%20profit-taking%2C%20and%20jitters%20about%20competition%20sparked%20the%20latest%20rout.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EYet%2C%20analysts%20at%20Bank%20of%20America%20and%20UBS%20say%20there%20are%20reasons%20to%20stick%20with%20the%20AI%20hardware%20trade.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJuly%20has%20been%20volatile%20for%20chip%20makers%2C%20but%20analysts%20say%20it's%20worth%20holding%20on%20and%20sticking%20with%20AI%20hardware%20makers%20through%20the%20swings.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20red-hot%20corner%20of%20the%20AI%20trade%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20volatility%20this%20month.%20Profit-taking%20after%20months%20of%20gains%2C%20competition%20from%20AI%20models%20in%20China%2C%20and%20an%20unclear%20interest%20rate%20outlook%20helped%20push%20the%20chip%20sector%20into%20a%20bear%20market%20last%20week.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Wall%20Street%20analysts%20say%20stick%20with%20it%2C%20because%20the%20AI%20market%20is%20still%20strong%20despite%20recent%20scares.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLatest%20releases%20in%20open-source%20models%2C%20including%20China's%20Kimi%20K3%20launched%20July%2016%2C%20reinforce%20our%20bullish%20thesis%20on%20memory%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Bank%20of%20America.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20high%20level%2C%20we%20view%20the%20aggressive%20Chinese%20open-model%20API%20pricing%20(up%20to%205-350x%20cheaper%20than%20Western%20models)%20as%20reflective%20of%20business-model%20choices%2C%20not%20necessarily%20reflective%20of%20hardware%20costs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoonshoot%20AI%2C%20the%20Chinese%20startup%20behind%20Kimi%20K3%2C%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkimi-k3-ai-model-moonshot-china-open-weights-benchmarks-pricing-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20focus%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20it%20released%20its%20model%20last%20week.%20Chip%20stocks%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-chip-selloff-kimi-moonshot-ai-rotation-soxx-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplunged%20on%20the%20news%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20release%20of%20DeepSeek's%20R1%2C%20another%20Chinese%20AI%20model%20that%20triggered%20a%20sharp%20selloff%20in%20January%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20initial%20decline%2C%20BofA%20noted%20that%20open-source%20models%20like%20Kimi%20K3%20from%20fast%20growing%20Chinese%20labs%20may%20hurt%20tech%20companies%20with%20similar%20products%2C%20they'll%20also%20create%20fresh%20demand%20for%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20frontier%20model%20labs%20are%20spending%20capital%20to%20grab%20share%2C%20the%20market%20is%20likely%20expanding%20its%20aggregate%20compute%20and%20memory%20capacity%20in%20the%20process%3B%20and%20every%20enterprise%20that%20downloads%20Qwen%2C%20GLM%2C%20Hunyuan%2C%20or%20MiMo%20instead%20of%20paying%20for%20Claude%20Opus%20creates%20a%20new%20customer-side%20memory%20footprint%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BofA%20analyst%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20competition%20from%20foreign%20AI%20developers%20weighs%20on%20demand%20from%20US%20frontier%20labs%2C%20there's%20no%20reason%20to%20expect%20a%20glut%20of%20high-end%20GPUs%20to%20flood%20the%20market%2C%20UBS%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUlrike%20Hoffmann-Burchardi%2C%20CIO%20of%20UBS%20Americas%2C%20recently%20wrote%20that%20her%20team%20doesn't%20see%20the%20recent%20bear-market%20decline%20in%20chip%20stocks%20reflective%20of%20potential%20oversupply.%20They're%20also%20not%20worried%20about%20hyperscalers%20scaling%20back%20on%20AI%20capex%20if%20they%20don't%20start%20seeing%20a%20profit%20in%20the%20near%20term%2C%20even%20as%20AI%20chip%20costs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-chip-prices-chipflation-semiconductors-memory-stocks-kospi-ny-life-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econtinue%20to%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20giants%20view%20artificial%20intelligence%20as%20a%20winner-takes-all%2C%20existential%20battle%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20a%20note%20to%20investors.%20%26quot%3BEven%20if%20immediate%20financial%20returns%20are%20low%2C%20companies%20will%20continue%20buying%20hardware%20to%20prevent%20rivals%20from%20gaining%20a%20permanent%20technological%20advantage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20BofA%2C%20Hoffmann-Burchardi%20added%20that%20UBS%20sees%20new%20AI%20models%20like%20Kimi%20K3%20and%20Inkling%20from%20Thinking%20Machines%2C%20creating%20more%20growth%20opportunities%20for%20AI%20hardware%20makers%2C%20as%20competition%20spurs%20heightened%20demand%20for%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchip-stocks-ai-hardware-kimi-k3-ubs-bofa-wall-street-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784662539000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5fbbdb54f9875261777d25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchip-stocks-ai-hardware-kimi-k3-ubs-bofa-wall-street-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20chip%20trade%20stumbled%20into%20a%20bear%20market%20this%20month%2C%20but%20analysts%20at%20BofA%20and%20UBS%20say%20that%20hardware%20makers%20will%20see%20even%20more%20demand%20going%20forward.%22%2C%22autho