ear-old%20mom%20felt%20out%20of%20breath%20while%20talking.%20It%20turns%20out%20she%20had%20stage%204%20lung%20cancer%2C%20despite%20never%20smoking.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smiling%20person%20wearing%20black%20glasses%20sits%20in%20front%20of%20green%20hydrangea%20leaves%20and%20purple%20flowers.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5a4f5b54f987526177689b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESummer%20Farmen%20is%20a%20six-year%20survivor%20of%20a%20rare%20lung%20cancer%20and%20now%20helps%20advocate%20for%20more%20research%20and%20education%20on%20the%20disease.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Summer%20Farmen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESummer%20Farmen%2C%20a%20mom%20of%20three%2C%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20rare%20form%20of%20lung%20cancer%20despite%20never%20smoking.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20condition%2C%20known%20as%20alk-positive%20lung%20cancer%2C%20inspired%20her%20to%20become%20an%20advocate%20to%20give%20back.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFarmen%20is%20celebrating%20six%20years%20as%20a%20survivor%20thanks%20to%20targeted%20therapy%20medications%20that%20fight%20tumors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Summer%20Farmen%20first%20noticed%20the%20shortness%20of%20breath%20and%20persistent%20tiredness%2C%20she%20didn't%20think%20much%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20early%202020%2C%20but%20COVID%20wasn't%20her%20first%20thought%2C%20since%20she%20otherwise%20felt%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20a%20month%2C%20she%20found%20herself%20choking%20and%20coughing%20during%20casual%20conversations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pennsylvania-based%20mom%20of%20three%20was%20used%20to%20taking%20extra%20care%20of%20herself%2C%20since%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20are%20primary%20caregivers%20for%20their%20son%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmy-son-has-cerebral-palsy-public-school-wont-accommodate-him-2023-8%5C%22%20t