0months%20to%20live%2C%20maybe%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20with%20good%20luck.%20More%20than%20six%20years%20later%2C%20at%20age%2050%2C%20Farmen%20is%20not%20just%20surviving%20but%20thriving.%20She%20used%20her%20experiences%20as%20a%20patient%20to%20advocate%20for%20more%20and%20better%20research%20to%20help%20others%20facing%20the%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20therapeutic%20to%20give%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20educating%20and%20empowering%20patients%20that%20you're%20not%20just%20riding%20along%20for%20this%2C%20you're%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat.%20Make%20your%20voice%20heard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c54f2925-4ce1-4be6-b355-e2f1b129b848%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20rare%20genetic%20mutation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20ending%20up%20in%20the%20ER%2C%20the%20last%20thing%20Farmen%20expected%20was%20to%20celebrate%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-shoulder-pain-lung-cancer-spread-symptoms-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elung%20cancer%20diagnosis%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20that's%20exactly%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20doctors%20feared%20her%20cancer%20had%20spread%20from%20another%20organ%2C%20such%20as%20her%20uterus%2C%20and%20could%20be%20terminal.%20An%20end-stage%20diagnosis%20would%20mean%20the%20only%20treatment%20options%20would%20be%20to%20keep%20Farmen%20comfortable%20through%20her%20final%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20lung%20cancer%20is%20one%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolon-cancer-leading-cause-cancer-death-under-50-shocking-experts-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edeadliest%20cancers%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Farmen%20was%20diagnosed%20alk-positive%2C%20a%20specific%20subtype%20that's%20highly%20treatable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20the%20call%20that%20it%20was%20lung%20cancer%2C%20and%20my%20dad%20and%20I%20are%20in%20the%20front%20yard%20hugging%20and%20crying.%20We're%20so%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20specific%20form%20of%20cancer%20is%20caused%20by%20a%20gene%20mutation%20that%20occurs%20during%20the%20patient's%20lifetime%2C%20so%20it%20can't%20be%20passed%20down%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20responds%20well%20to%20targeted%20therapy%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-cancer-innovations-asco-2025-exercise-as-drug-astra-zeneca-early-treatment-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprecision%20cancer%20treatment%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20blocks%20the%20cancer's%20fuel%20sources%2C%20such%20as%20proteins%2C%20to%20prevent%20tumors%20from%20growing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarmen's%20treatment%20plan%20included%20medications%20called%20tyrosine%20kinase%20inhibitors%20that%20work%20by%20interrupting%20signals%20that%20tell%20cancer%20cells%20to%20grow%20and%20divide%20uncontrollably.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Farmen%20said%20she's%20generally%20an%20optimist%2C%20the%20treatment%20process%20%26quot%3Bwasn't%20all%20sunshine.%26quot%3B%20She%20was%20afraid%20of%20never%20teaching%20her%20son%20to%20drive%20or%20missing%20her%20daughter's%20high%20school%20graduation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Group%20poses%20with%20a%20graduate%20in%20blue%20cap%20and%20gown%20outside%20a%20Penn%20State%20stadium%20on%20a%20sunny%20day.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5fafd1548c9c486b30e9cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFarmen%20with%20her%20husband%2C%20daughter%2C%20and%20two%20sons.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Summer%20Farmen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20went%20to%20dark%20places.%20I%20was%20in%20the%20fetal%20position%20several%20times%2C%20but%20I'd%20never%20let%20myself%20stay%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20major%20turning%20point%20as%20she%20underwent%20treatment%20was%20finding%20support%20groups%20with%20other%20alk-positive%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20lifeline%20immediately.%20You're%20finding%20out%20about%20different%20patient%20experiences.%20You're%20getting%20validation%2C%26quot%3B%20Farmen%20said.%20%26quot%3BRight%20away%20in%20the%20beginning%2C%20I'm%20learning%20about%20strength%20and%20adversity%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20patient%20preferences%2C%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20patient%20voice.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eb92e9ed-dc7a-4705-a84a-dbe308e3a2e6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20patient%20to%20advocate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFarmen's%20journey%20into%20the%20alk-positive%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F24-year-old-shocking-cancer-diagnosis-menopause-symptoms-side-effect-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecancer%20support%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20started%20with%20an%20art%20therapy%20class%20on%20Zoom.%20Before%20long%2C%20she%20was%20helping%20to%20expand%20the%20program%20and%20organizing%20educational%20sessions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSoon%20after%20I%20became%20involved%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20give%20back.%20I%20had%20to%20help%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20nonprofit%20behind%20the%20programs%2C%20Alk%20Positive%20Inc.%2C%20funds%20cancer%20research%20to%20improve%20patients'%20quality%20of%20life%20while%20providing%20resources%20such%20as%20support%20groups%20and%20clinical%20trial%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarmen%20is%20now%20the%20organization's%20vice%20president%20and%20a%20contributor%20to%20a%20recent%20study%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0169500226005106%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejournal%20Lung%20Cancer%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20people%20pose%20together%20in%20front%20of%20a%20marble%20wall%2C%20one%20wearing%20a%20black%20suit%20with%20a%20white%20boutonniere.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5a68bbce52cb26b8390c9f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFarmen%20with%20her%20son%20Harrison.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Summer%20Farmen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20research%20focused%20on%20patient%20and%20caregiver%20preferences%20in%20balancing%20the%20potential%20benefits%20and%20side%20effects%20of%20treatment%20options%2C%20a%20key%20issue%20in%20the%20increasingly%20personalized%20world%20of%20cancer%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarmen%20said%20that%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-started-company-while-battling-stage-4-lung-cancer-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecancer%20survivor%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20back%20has%20helped%20her%20come%20to%20terms%20with%20some%20of%20the%20psychological%20toll.%20The%20physical%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foncologist-diagnosed-breast-cancer-no-symptoms-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eemotional%20strain%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20wouldn't%20pick%20me%20out%20of%20a%20group%20as%20a%20stage%20four%20lung%20cancer%20patient%2C%20but%20there%20are%20debilitating%20side%20effects%20that%20everybody%20experiences%20differently%20from%20these%20life-extending%20treatments%20that%20we're%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20still%20have%20a%20stage%20four%20cancer%20diagnosis.%20I%20still%20have%20scans%20every%20three%20months.%20It's%20not%20if%20my%20cancer%20progresses%2C%20it's%20when%20my%20cancer%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20Farmen%2C%20who%20turned%2050%20in%20April%2C%20is%20busy%20celebrating%20five%20decades%20of%20being%20alive.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20so%20lucky%20to%20be%2050.%20I'm%20so%20happy%20to%20be%20here.%20Growing%20old%20is%20a%20privilege%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F44-year-old-woman-trouble-breathing-stage-4-lung-cancer-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784656202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5a68d1ce52cb26b8390ca0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F44-year-old-woman-trouble-breathing-stage-4-lung-cancer-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20busy%20mom%20of%20three%20developed%20a%20persistent%20cough%20and%20had%20trouble%20breathing%2C%20despite%20never%20smoking.%20She%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20a%20rare%20form%20of%20lung%20cancer.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22glandsverk%40insider.com%20(Gabby%20Landsverk)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20'open'%20AI%20is%20a%20terrible%20business%2C%20and%20nothing%20like%20open-source%20software%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223209%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Executives%20from%20artificial%20intelligence%20company%20Zhipu%20AI%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Knowledge%20Atlas%20Technology%2C%20semiconductor%20company%20Shanghai%20Iluvatar%20CoreX%20and%20surgical%20robotics%20company%20Shenzhen%20Edge%20Medical%20attend%20a%20listing%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20Stock%20Exchange%2C%20in%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20China%20January%208%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5f9ed4ce52cb26b8391e44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EZ.ai%20executives%20attend%20a%20listing%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Hong%20Kong%20Stock%20Exchange.%3Cp%3EKANE%20WU%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EZhipu's%20open-weight%20AI%20model%20GLM%205.2%20wow%20developers%2C%20but%20its%20stock%20has%20plunged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpen-source%20software%20benefits%20from%20easy%2C%20cheap%20distribution.%20Open-weight%20AI%20is%20very%20different.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOther%20companies%20often%20run%20Chinese%20open-weight%20models.%20That's%20where%20the%20money%20is%20made.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20angst%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-china-internet-is-saying-about-moonshot-kimi-model-k3-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChina's%20latest%20AI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20missing%20an%20important%20business%20fact%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-gpt-oss-open-weight-llm-ai-model-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eopen%20weight%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20AI%20is%20not%20the%20same%20thing%20as%20open-source%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-llama-2-ai-model-not-open-source-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpen-source%3C%2Fa%3E%20software%2C%20where%20the%20code%20is%20freely%20shared%2C%20can%20be%20an%20amazing%20business.%20Think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ibm-and-red-hat-deal-came-together-2018-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERed%20Hat%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20IBM%20bought%20for%20%2434%20billion.%20Open-weight%20AI%20models%20are%20different%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20so%20far%2C%20they're%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20terrible%20business.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20Z.ai%2C%20also%20known%20as%20Zhipu.%20It's%20publicly%20traded%2C%20so%20we%20can%20see%20its%20finances.%20Last%20year%2C%20the%20Chinese%20company%20lost%20almost%20%24500%20million%20on%20revenue%20of%20about%20%24107%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhipu%20is%20the%20lab%20behind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-glm-5-2-chinese-ai-coding-model-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGLM%205.2%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20open-weight%20AI%20model%20that%20wowed%20the%20industry%20when%20it%20launched%20last%20month.%20You%20might%20expect%20the%20stock%20to%20have%20soared.%20Instead%2C%20Zhipu%20shares%20have%20plunged%20more%20than%2040%25%20over%20the%20past%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftreasury-secretary-chinese-ai-open-source-sanctions-kimi-k3-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMiniMax%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20only%20other%20independent%20Chinese%20AI%20labs%20that's%20publicly%20traded%2C%20lost%20%24250%20million%20last%20year%20on%20revenue%20of%20just%20%2479%20million.%20Its%20shares%20have%20fallen%20more%20than%2050%25%20in%20the%20past%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpen-weight%20models%20have%20a%20challenging%20path%20to%20making%20a%20profit%2C%26quot%3B%20William%20Blair%20analyst%20Arjun%20Bhatia%20wrote%20in%20a%20recent%20note%20to%20investors%2C%20in%20the%20understatement%20of%20the%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec7c48a7-8449-4776-a0fc-30458c22138f%5C%22%3EOpen-weight%20AI%20isn't%20open-source%20software%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20difference%20comes%20down%20to%20economics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoftware%20can%20be%20distributed%20almost%20for%20free.%20Once%20it's%20written%2C%20sending%20another%20customer%20a%20copy%20costs%20practically%20nothing.%20Profit%20margins%20improve%20as%20software%20companies%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20doesn't%20work%20that%20way.%20Every%20answer%20requires%20expensive%20chips%2C%20electricity%2C%20and%20data-center%20capacity.%20The%20next%20unit%20of%20software%20is%20nearly%20free%3B%20the%20next%20unit%20of%20intelligence%20is%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkimi-k3-ai-model-moonshot-investors-alibaba-cloud-tencent-stock-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMoonshot%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20another%20Chinese%20lab%2C%20illustrated%20the%20problem%20last%20week.%20Its%20new%20Kimi%20K3%20open-weight%20model%20impressed%20the%20industry%20with%20frontier-level%20performance.%20But%20days%20after%20launch%2C%20the%20company%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoonshot-kimi-ai-paused-new-users-popularity-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehalt%20new%20customer%20sign-ups%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20didn't%20have%20enough%20computing%20power%20to%20run%20the%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Moonshot%20were%20selling%20traditional%20software%2C%20adding%20millions%20of%20users%20would%20be%20relatively%20easy.%20Instead%2C%20every%20new%20customer%20increases%20the%20company's%20infrastructure%20bill%2C%20capping%20its%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8bf315e-dd10-40fd-9990-f3cffea559b7%5C%22%3ESomeone%20else%20captures%20the%20profits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20way%20open-weight%20AI%20models%20are%20run%2C%20a%20process%20known%20as%20inference%2C%20makes%20the%20business%20situation%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpen-weight%20AI%20labs%20give%20outsiders%20their%20models'%20trained%20numerical%20parameters%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20download%20and%20run%20them.%20(Parameters%20are%20like%20tiny%20numerical%20dials%20inside%20a%20model's%20brain%20that%20determine%20how%20these%20systems%20learn%20from%20data%20and%20what%20outputs%20they%20produce).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20that%2C%20these%20models%20are%20usually%20run%20by%20other%20companies%2C%20such%20as%20cloud%20giants%20Amazon%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20Google%2C%20Oracle%2C%20and%20Alibaba.%20There%20are%20also%20specialist%20providers%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffireworks-ai-surge-ceo-lin-qiao-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFireworks%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Baseten%2C%20although%20they%20largely%20rent%20capacity%20from%20the%20big%20cloud%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20can%20also%20download%20these%20open%20weights%20and%20run%20the%20models%20themselves.%20Or%2C%20they%20can%20also%20use%20the%20Chinese%20model%20maker's%20own%20inference%20service%2C%20but%20in%20the%20Western%20world%2C%20most%20corporate%20customers%20don't%20do%20that%20for%20data%20security%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20that%20last%20option%20reliably%20generates%20real%20revenue%20for%20the%20model%20creator.%20In%20the%20other%20three%20cases%2C%20the%20AI%20lab%20that%20spent%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20building%20the%20model%20may%20receive%20little%20or%20no%20ongoing%20revenue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20leaves%20the%20model%20makers%20in%20a%20difficult%20position.%20They've%20paid%20heavily%20to%20train%20the%20systems%2C%20then%20given%20away%20the%20key%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20wonder%20Alibaba's%20stock%20is%20up%20about%2013%25%20over%20the%20past%20month%2C%20while%20AI%20labs%20Zhipu%20and%20MiniMax%20have%20been%20crushed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269399632-6e81-4d19-bdc9-284270a2f683%5C%22%3ENot%20Red%20Hat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20open-source%20software%2C%20open-weight%20models%20do%20not%20generate%20significant%20sums%20of%20revenue%20by%20selling%20support%2C%20services%2C%20and%20enterprise%20editions%20around%20the%20free%20offering%20(the%20Red%20Hat%20playbook)%2C%26quot%3B%20William%20Blair's%20Bhatia%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20they%20primarily%20generate%20revenue%20by%20hosting%20the%20model%20and%20selling%20inference%20compute.%20But%20inference%20workloads%20will%20flow%20to%20whoever%20can%20operate%20the%20inference%20infrastructure%20most%20efficiently%2C%20and%20this%20is%20usually%20not%20the%20model%20provider%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analyst%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERaimo%20Lenshow%2C%20an%20analyst%20at%20Barclays%2C%20recently%20came%20back%20from%20China%20after%20researching%20the%20country's%20AI%20sector.%20He%20reached%20a%20similar%20conclusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIntense%20domestic%20competition%20has%20also%20led%20to%20more%20aggressive%20pricing%20competition%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20analyst%20told%20investors.%20%26quot%3BSome%20major%20models%20remain%20open-source%20or%20open-weight%2C%20accelerating%20the%20pricing%20pressure%20throughout%20the%20system.%20While%20this%20helps%20drive%20faster%20commercialization%2C%20it%20is%20also%20adding%20uncertainty%20to%20long-term%20profitability%20for%20those%20AI%20labs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243a8a7cf-777c-41fd-b882-aab0a1d15295%5C%22%3ESo%20why%20give%20the%20models%20away%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpen%20technology%20has%20long%20been%20a%20strategy%20for%20challengers%20trying%20to%20catch%20market%20leaders.%20A%20late%20starter%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20match%20a%20leader's%20customers%20or%20distribution%2C%20but%20it%20can%20spread%20its%20technology%20widely%2C%20attract%20developers%2C%20and%20make%20the%20leader's%20product%20harder%20to%20sell%20at%20premium%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20may%20be%20exactly%20what%20China%20and%20its%20AI%20labs%20are%20trying%20to%20do.%20Open-weight%20models%20put%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdistillation-problem-ai-industry-anthropic-openai-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epressure%20on%20OpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20other%20US%20leaders%20by%20offering%20capable%20alternatives%20at%20lower%20prices.%20Even%20if%20the%20Chinese%20labs%20make%20little%20money%20themselves%2C%20they%20can%20force%20American%20competitors%20to%20cut%20prices%20and%20make%20it%20harder%20to%20recover%20the%20billions%20they%20spend%20training%20new%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBhatia%20said%20Chinese%20labs%20may%20be%20releasing%20open-weight%20models%20with%20%26quot%3Blittle%20regard%20for%20near-term%20profitability.%26quot%3B%20In%20his%20view%2C%20openness%20can%20turn%20advanced%20AI%20into%20a%20commodity%2C%20weakening%20the%20business%20model%20of%20US%20companies%20that%20keep%20their%20technology%20closed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20payoff%20for%20the%20Chinese%20labs%20may%20come%20much%20later%20%E2%80%94%20or%20may%20be%20less%20important%20than%20the%20broader%20strategic%20benefit%20to%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChina's%20leadership%20is%20now%20openly%20encouraging%20that%20strategy.%20In%20a%20recent%20speech%20in%20Shanghai%2C%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20said%20countries%20should%20seize%20the%20opportunity%20to%20encourage%20%26quot%3Bopen-source%2C%20openness%2C%20collaboration%2C%20and%20sharing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20like%20that%20is%20more%20than%20a%20casual%20policy%20suggestion.%20Chinese%20technology%20companies%20are%20expected%20to%20align%20with%20the%20government's%20strategic%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Xi%20put%20openness%20at%20the%20center%20of%20China's%20AI%20strategy%2C%20companies%20such%20as%20Moonshot%2C%20Zhipu%2C%20and%20MiniMax%20are%20likely%20to%20face%20strong%20pressure%20to%20follow%20that%20direction%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20it%20makes%20their%20own%20path%20to%20profit%20much%20harder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-ai-boom-terrible-business-open-weight-models-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784655797000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5f9eb6548c9c486b30e90f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-ai-boom-terrible-business-open-weight-models-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China's%20AI%20models%20are%20impressing%20developers%20but%20losing%20investors.%20The%20problem%3F%20Open-weight%20AI%20is%20a%20much%20worse%20business%20than%20open-source%20software.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abarr%40businessinsider.com%20(Alistair%20Barr)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amazon%20taps%20Alexa%20executive%20as%20Leo%20satellite%20business%E2%80%99s%20first%20finance%20VP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amazon%20Leo%20Satellite%20Connectivity%20signage%20is%20displayed%20during%20the%20annual%20Consumer%20Electronics%20Show%20(CES)%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Nevada%20on%20January%206%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5f9da9ce52cb26b8391e2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAmazon%20Leo%20Satellite%20Connectivity%20signage%20is%20displayed%20during%20the%20annual%20Consumer%20Electronics%20Show%20(CES)%20in%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Nevada%20on%20January%206%2C%202026.%3Cp%3EPatrick%20T.%20Fallon%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMike%20Recupero%20is%20the%20first%20VP%20of%20finance%20for%20Amazon's%20Leo%20satellite%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%20is%20putting%20together%20a%20seasoned%20leadership%20team%20for%20Leo.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAmazon%20expects%20Leo%20to%20generate%20meaningful%20growth%20and%20returns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-managers-challenge-automated-staffing-decisions-warehouse-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Leo%20satellite%20business%20has%20appointed%20its%20first%20dedicated%20finance%20VP%2C%20another%20sign%20the%20company%20is%20building%20the%20satellite%20venture%20into%20a%20more%20independent%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMike%20Recupero%2C%20who%20most%20recently%20served%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-moonraker-project-alexa-agentic-cost-2026-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlexa's%3C%2Fa%3E%20finance%20chief%2C%20was%20named%20Leo's%20VP%20of%20finance%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20according%20to%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20move.%20The%20newly%20created%20role%20makes%20him%20the%20first%20VP%20solely%20overseeing%20Leo's%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20Recupero%20spent%20about%20a%20year%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-ryan-cohen-compensation-ceo-pay-deal-ebay-acquisition-takeover-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGameStop's%3C%2Fa%3E%20CFO%20after%20serving%20as%20finance%20chief%20for%20several%20Amazon%20businesses%2C%20including%20Prime%20Video%20and%20North%20America%20retail.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20now%2C%20Leo's%20finances%20were%20overseen%20by%20executives%20who%20also%20managed%20Alexa%2C%20supported%20by%20more%20junior%20finance%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20appointment%20reflects%20how%20Amazon%20is%20assembling%20a%20seasoned%20leadership%20team%20around%20Leo%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Project%20Kuiper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20Leo%20has%20also%20recruited%20former%20GitLab%20chief%20revenue%20officer%20Chris%20Weber%20as%20vice%20president%20of%20sales%20and%20marketing%20and%20former%20T-Mobile%20executive%20Clint%20Patterson%20as%20chief%20marketing%20officer.%20VP%20of%20technology%20Rajeev%20Badyal%20leads%20the%20overall%20Leo%20business%20and%20reports%20to%20Panos%20Panay%2C%20SVP%20of%20devices%2C%20Alexa%2C%20and%20Leo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecupero%20will%20primarily%20oversee%20Leo's%20multibillion-dollar%20infrastructure%20buildout%2C%20including%20satellite%20manufacturing%20and%20launches%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20integration%20of%20Globalstar%2C%20the%20satellite%20communications%20company%20Amazon%20is%20acquiring%20for%20%2411.6%20billion%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmit%20Singh%20has%20replaced%20Recupero%20as%20Alexa's%20finance%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeo%20is%20one%20of%20Amazon's%20biggest%20long-term%20bets%20beyond%20its%20core%20retail%20and%20cloud%20businesses.%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20previously%20said%20Leo%20already%20had%20a%20series%20of%20revenue%20commitments%20from%20enterprise%20and%20government%20customers%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20generate%20meaningful%20growth%20and%20returns%20for%20Amazon.%20The%20company%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20Leo%20has%20completed%2014%20missions%20and%20launched%20396%20satellites%20so%20far%2C%20making%20it%20the%20third-largest%20satellite%20constellation%20in%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWall%20Street%20is%20also%20growing%20more%20bullish%20on%20the%20business.%20Bank%20of%20America%20recently%20estimated%20Leo%20could%20generate%20%2420%20billion%20to%20%2425%20billion%20in%20annual%20revenue%20by%202032%20and%20eventually%20be%20worth%20%24200%20billion%20to%20%24275%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20enthusiasm%20has%20not%20eliminated%20the%20risks.%20A%20Blue%20Origin%20rocket%20that%20Amazon%20plans%20to%20use%20for%20future%20Leo%20missions%20exploded%20during%20a%20ground%20test%20in%20June.%20Leo's%20VP%20Badyal%20sought%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-blue-origin-rocket-explosion-memo-leo-starlink-spacex-2026-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereassure%3C%2Fa%3E%20employees%20at%20the%20time%2C%20saying%20such%20setbacks%20are%20an%20expected%20part%20of%20spaceflight%20and%20that%20the%20company%20would%20continue%20pressing%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aekim%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eekim%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%2C%20Telegram%2C%20or%20WhatsApp%20at%20650-942-3061.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%2