%22Corner's%20team%20is%20building%20a%20social%20mapping%20app%20for%20Gen%20Z.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5f7c4654f98752617779ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221094%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECorner's%20team%20is%20building%20a%20social%20mapping%20app%20for%20Gen%20Z.%3Cp%3ESydney%20Bradley%2FBI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECorner%2C%20a%20social%20mapping%20startup%20that%20helps%20people%20find%20local%20spots%2C%20has%20doubled%20its%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20New%20York-based%20startup%20has%20raised%20%247.5%20million%2C%20the%20company%20confirmed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20one%20of%20many%20new%20social%20media%20startups%20trying%20to%20break%20through.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20a%20really%20good%20restaurant%20or%20bar%20takes%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-social-app-corner-google-maps-gen-z-ai-events-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECorner%2C%20a%20startup%3C%2Fa%3E%20looking%20to%20make%20that%20process%20easier%2C%20has%20raised%20more%20capital%20to%20stake%20its%20claim%20in%20the%20map%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorner%2C%20which%20was%20founded%20in%202022%2C%20is%20a%20social-mapping%20app%20targeting%20Gen%20Z%20users%20who%20want%20to%20meet%20up%20in%20real%20life.%20In%20the%20app%2C%20users%20can%20leave%20reviews%2C%20share%20photos%2C%20and%20curate%20lists.%20Locations%20are%20added%20to%20Corner's%20map%20only%20when%20a%20user%20saves%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20platform%20has%20more%20than%20250%2C000%20users%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0primarily%20in%20New%20York%20and%20Europe%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0across%20425%20cities%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20has%20nearly%20doubled%20its%20total%20funding%20since%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20Corner%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20had%20raised%20%243.75%20million%20across%20two%20rounds%20from%20VC%20funds%20including%20Abstract%20Ventures%2C%20Tapestry%2C%20and%201517.%20The%20startup%20also%20has%20angel%20investors%2C%20like%20Partiful's%20cofounder%20Shreya%20Murthy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York-based%20startup%20has%20raised%20new%20funding%20since%2C%20with%20total%20funding%20reaching%20%247.5%20million%2C%20Corner%20confirmed.%20The%20startup%20is%20gearing%20up%20to%20raise%20a%20Series%20A%20round.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorner%20isn't%20the%20only%20app%20trying%20to%20make%20waves%20in%20the%20social-mapping%20and%20restaurant-saving%20categories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeli%2C%20a%20rival%20app%20for%20saving%20and%20sharing%20restaurants%2C%20had%20raised%20%2412%20million%20in%20venture%20capital%20as%20of%20June%202025%2C%20the%20company%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Apps%20like%20Amo's%20Bump%2C%20a%20social%20app%20for%20tracking%20your%20friends%2C%20are%20also%20gaining%20steam.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Corner%20has%20to%20compete%20with%20larger%20players%20like%20Google%20Maps%2C%20Apple%20Maps%2C%20and%20Yelp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorner%20has%20carved%20out%20a%20following%20on%20social%20media%20as%20it%20grows%20its%20platform%20and%20business.%20Its%20digital%20magazine%20has%20over%2091%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-startup-founders-selfie-sticks-venture-funding-influencers-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEliza%20Wu%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Jake%20Xia%2C%20Corner's%20cofounders%2C%20have%20also%20become%20faces%20of%20the%20brand%20on%20social.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Corner%20product%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5f885fce52cb26b8391cd6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECorner%20is%20a%20social%20map%20for%20saving%20and%20sharing%20local%20spots.%3Cp%3ECorner%3B%20Apple%20App%20Store%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2209111b0d-6a6d-4724-9356-da51670da748%5C%22%3EA%20map%20with%20personalized%20recommendations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20Corner%20rolled%20out%20an%20overhauled%20search%20feature%20that%20leverages%20AI%20to%20suggest%20recommendations%20based%20on%20Corner%20reviews%20and%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20proprietary%20dataset%20powers%20true%20personalization%20instead%20of%20virality-based%20recommendations%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Corner%20CEO%20Wu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECorner's%20been%20experimenting%20with%20new%20features%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I've%20noticed%20Corner%20will%20let%20me%20know%20when%20a%20reservation%20opens%20up%20at%20a%20restaurant%20I've%20saved.%20The%20app%20also%20now%20lets%20you%20add%20bookings%20and%20events%2C%20provides%20a%20round-up%20of%20places%20that%20people%20%E2%80%94%20including%20your%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20are%20raving%20about%2C%20and%20offers%20age-%20and%20location-based%20suggestions%20on%20where%20to%20go%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20everything%20else%20that%20I've%20seen%2C%20and%20I've%20seen%20this%20idea%20tried%20a%20dozen%20times%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20this%20was%20the%20best%20execution%20I'd%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20Abstract%20Ventures'%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fseed-100-best-early-stage-vc-investors-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERamtin%20Naimi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Corner%20investor%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-map-startup-corner-raised-seven-million-venture-capital-genz-2026-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1784653382000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a5f7c4654f98752617779ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsocial-map-startup-corner-raised-seven-million-venture-capital-genz-2026-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%2